packages at runtime. Their licenses are permissive or weak-copyleft and are
compatible with this project's MIT license. Run `pip-licenses` for the full,
current list with versions.

Runtime dependencies and license families:
  - FastAPI, Starlette, Uvicorn, Pydantic ......... MIT
  - httpx, pdfplumber, pypdf, pytesseract ......... MIT / BSD
  - pypdfium2 .................................... Apache-2.0 / BSD-3-Clause
    (PDF rendering; a permissive replacement for the AGPL-licensed PyMuPDF)
  - Pillow ....................................... MIT-CMU
  - arabic-reshaper .............................. MIT
  - python-bidi .................................. LGPL-3.0 (used unmodified)
  - python-docx .................................. MIT

Development-only tooling (not distributed with the service):
